Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是汐宮栞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正被一種巨大而又莫名其妙的「怪異」纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種詭異的感覺時刻困擾著我的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我不敢放鬆絲毫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞高祭用的影印本小說寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還  還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的「一點」也太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是後天早上還不能提交上來  那就不用你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實已經有所察覺  這種「怪異」的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是被世上的普通男女稱為戀  戀…戀愛的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在故事中描述得有時甜蜜  有時可愛  有時悲傷的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的感受卻不是上面的任何一種
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介入我的小說之中的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男人摟摟抱抱的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男扮女裝還大笑不止的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和當初我在圖書館閉關不出時拯救了我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是同一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這還真是夠離譜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一個邂逅的男人竟然是那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒錯  變態  女裝癖的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓我怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而讓我最無法原諒的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男人是個不守承諾的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明說好了會來看我寫的小說的續章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我一整天都在等他卻沒見人來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是個倒錯變態男的話還有得救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可一個不守承諾的倒錯變態男根本無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是和那樣的男人…接吻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  直到不久前我對這事一點印象都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我難道是個將人生中初次接吻這種大事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都輕易忘掉的大呆瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是從哪進來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是哪來的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是汐宮栞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正被一種莫名其妙的「怪異」纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅的神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我去死一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.53,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look up at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.16,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Like a bird without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.56,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}If you want to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.92,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Feel your breeze, release yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.44,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.03,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.39,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Every time you try
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:29.37,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Find something, believe yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.89,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}My mission is gonna be a tough one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.49,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I know it's not a game anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.55,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I swear that I'll never fail again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.77,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}'Cuz don't wanna regret anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.27,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear I'm calling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.98,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I just wanna feel you
