Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:08.15,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You know I won't surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.96,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Never surrender
